                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5 class="card-title">Dashboard</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">The Dashboard is a comprehensive control panel that allows you
                                        to manage all your cybersecurity activities from a central location. With
                                        real-time data and alerts, you can quickly assess the security status of your
                                        system. Monitor system performance and promptly respond to significant security
                                        incidents.</p>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">News</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">The News page helps you stay up-to-date with the latest
                                        cybersecurity news and trends. By keeping informed about cyber threats and
                                        security vulnerabilities, you can take the necessary precautions to protect your
                                        system. The news is curated by industry experts and regularly updated.</p>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">IP Logs</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">The IP Logs page records all incoming and outgoing IP addresses
                                        on your system. This allows you to monitor network traffic, detect abnormal
                                        activities, and take proactive measures against potential threats. Detailed
                                        analyses of IP logs help you review past events and refine your security
                                        strategies.</p>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">Eventlog</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">The Eventlog page retrieves, analyzes, and categorizes all logs
                                        from your local computer. This enables users to easily distinguish between
                                        different types of events and detect potential threats more quickly and
                                        effectively. Eventlog provides a chronological record of security incidents,
                                        allowing for detailed examination and analysis.</p>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">File Watchdog</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">The File Watchdog page monitors and records any changes
                                        occurring in a specified file path. By tracking file changes, you can instantly
                                        detect unauthorized access or modifications and take necessary actions. The file
                                        path can be easily updated via a POST request, offering flexibility and a
                                        user-friendly experience.</p>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">Virus Total</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">The Virus Total page allows you to investigate potential
                                        threats using the hash codes of your files. It performs a comprehensive virus
                                        scan to determine the safety of files and informs you of any possible threats.
                                        This proactive measure helps you identify and mitigate harmful files before they
                                        can damage your system.</p>
                                </div>
